<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>مِنْ الْأَخْلَاقِ الْحَمِيدَةِ الْإِحْسَان<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c5">قَالَ تَعَالَى:</span> <span class="c3">{وَأَحْسِنُوا إِنَّ اللهَ يُحِبُّ الْمُحْسِنِينَ}</span> <span class="c2">(١)</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c5">وَقَالَ تَعَالَى:</span> <span class="c3">{إِنَّ رَحْمَتَ اللهِ قَرِيبٌ مِنَ الْمُحْسِنِينَ}</span> <span class="c2">(٢)</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>وَقَالَ تَعَالَى <span class="c3">{إِنَّهُ مَنْ يَتَّقِ وَيَصْبِرْ فَإِنَّ اللهَ لَا يُضِيعُ أَجْرَ الْمُحْسِنِينَ}</span> <span class="c2">(٣)</span><a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c5">وَقَالَ تَعَالَى:</span> <span class="c3">{إِنَّ اللهَ مَعَ الَّذِينَ اتَّقَوْا , وَالَّذِينَ هُمْ مُحْسِنُونَ}</span> <span class="c2">(٤)</span><a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c5">وَقَالَ تَعَالَى:</span> <span class="c3">{وَالَّذِينَ جَاهَدُوا فِينَا لَنَهْدِيَنَّهُمْ سُبُلَنَا , وَإِنَّ اللهَ لَمَعَ الْمُحْسِنِينَ}</span> <span class="c2">(٥)</span><a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<hr>
<p class="hamesh">(١) [البقرة: ١٩٥]<br>(٢) [الأعراف: ٥٦]<br>(٣) [يوسف: ٩٠]<br>(٤) [النحل: ١٢٨]<br>(٥) [العنكبوت: ٦٩]</p> </div>